   SNfactory Software we need but don't have:
   -----------------------------------------------------------------------
   -------- Search:
   -----------------------------------------------------------------------
   -------- NEAT field selection [3 wks] current moon avoidance future
   moon avoidance follow-up potential (e.g. visible last half of night for
   2 months) Maui field rotation [1 wk] NEAT image transfer monitor [1 - 4
   wks] speed interupts log alarm caching status and log switch to T1
   backup (Palomar) Candidate catalog cross-id (from NED & SIMBAD) [1 - 2
   wks] known redshift and other host galaxy parameters (size,
   orientation) QSO/variable star star forming galaxy Construction of
   historic NEAT lightcurves for all candidates [8 wks] Image-quality
   feedback [4 wks] Photometric bootstrap calibration (standard stars &
   image overlaps) [4 wks] Backup (databases, NEAT hdr info, etc.) [4 wks]
   (total 18 - 22 wks)
   -----------------------------------------------------------------------
   -------- Scheduling:
   -----------------------------------------------------------------------
   -------- Follow-up scheduler (can we use SPIKE?) [4 - 16 wks]
   N-telescopes current weather forecast future weather forecast current
   time available future time available current moon avoidance future moon
   avoidance candidate ranking active SN ranking (higher ranking if
   already invested) investment options (total 4 - 16 wks)
