   -------- Generic Follow-up implementation
   -----------------------------------------------------------------------
   -------- SNIFS observing script (see webpage description) [8 - 12 wks]
   Processing of SNIFS imaging data [8 - 12 wks] Automated field
   identification on-the-fly extinction estimatation (including web plots)
   on-the-fly cross calibration of imager and spectrograph (including web
   plots) Autoguider control [2 wks] Autoguider output [1 wk] flux
   variations --> photometric no not mean seeing / seeing distribution
   Environmental inputs (log in database or use header was database) [1 -
   4 wks] CSO H2O column Mauna Loa extinction local wind speed and
   direction humidty temperature (inside dome and outside) CCD temperature
   Cryotiger monitor/alarm [1 - 2 wks] (total 21 - 33 wks)
